title: ANIME Drawing BOX set 5-in-1
description:
http://ititli.com/images/wymB4aA.jpg

Drawing Anime BOX SET 5-in-1 is the perfect guide for everyone who wants to learn how to draw various Anime characters.

Step by step tutorials have been given along with high quality pictures. You will not feel intimidated by the drawings. In fact, the seemingly overwhelming anime characters are made easy for you in these books.
Go ahead reading and practicing with the books and you will be able to master drawing anime figures in just a few weeks.

Here is preview of what you will find in the BOX SET 5-in-1:

ANIME Drawing BOX set 5-in-1 by Li Shen, Jane Mackle, Yuka Hiramatsu
